data.description: Enjoy the serenity of living in a tight knit community where  neighbors become friends.  Say goodbye to shoveling snow and mowing the lawn.    The open floor plan, vaulted ceiling and  fireplace give the home a warm cozy feeling.  In the summer enjoy the private shady covered pergola that is enclosed for a small pet.  In the winter, work in the insulated garage or work from home where Loveland's fiber optic High Speed "Pulse" internet is installed. The home is located close to the private circle walking path and gazebo or stroll to Krohl Park.   This home in the sought after Circle Park subdivision has three bedrooms and is waiting a new owner. The low maintenance home won't disappoint.
